{% comment %}
  Brand override (perf): Horizon's type_*_font settings still point at Inter, but
  the brand layer (snippets/brand.liquid) hard-overrides all four --font-*--family
  vars to the Boring Foods fonts, so Inter never renders. Preloading it here fetched
  ~120 KB of unused woff2 on the critical path, competing with the LCP hero for early
  bandwidth. We intentionally preload nothing: the brand fonts are declared in the
  inline {% style %} block in <head> (discovered immediately, font-display: swap), so
  they need no preload, and skipping these hints frees early bandwidth for the hero.
  To restore Horizon's Inter preloads, repoint type_*_font to a custom font and revert.
{% endcomment %}
